        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/miami/scene_flamingo.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository bf60280b-9b3b-4837-a90e-8cbcfe46d515).Image",
        "Description": "No more Mr. Nice Mascot.\r\rYour boss Maxwell Rutter is about to fire you for &apos;conduct unbecoming of a team mascot&apos;. Grace Miller, Kronstadt&apos;s chief monkey wrench, is the one who blew the whistle on you. All of it lies.\r\rTake out the brains of the operation...literally, then give Miller a wake up call she&apos;ll never forget while doing some damage to her self righteous and unfairly advantaged team.\r\rThe mascot will get the last laugh.",
